[
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d0</span> (<i>Alef</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">Alas</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"2\" /> has <st data-num=\"05743\" class=\"\">covered</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st><n id=\"3\" /> with his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He has <st data-num=\"07993\" class=\"\">thrown down</st> the <st data-num=\"08597\" class=\"\">splendor</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st><p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st> to <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">protect</st><n id=\"5\" /> his <st data-num=\"01916 07272\">temple</st><n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">when</st> he displayed his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>.<n id=\"7\" /></p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d1</span> (<i>Bet</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808 02550\">mercilessly</st><n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04999\" class=\"\">homes</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\">Jacob\u2019s descendants</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">In his <st data-num=\"05678\" class=\"\">anger</st> he <st data-num=\"02040\" class=\"\">tore down</st><p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortified cities</st><n id=\"5\" /> of <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05060\" class=\"\">knocked</st> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> and <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">humiliated</st><p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> and its <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">rulers</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d2</span> (<i>Gimel</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">In <st data-num=\"02750\" class=\"\">fierce</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st><n id=\"1\" /> he <st data-num=\"01438\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"07161\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07725 0268\">withdrew</st> his <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right hand</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">as</st> the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">attacked</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">was</st> like a <st data-num=\"03852\" class=\"\">raging</st> <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> in the land of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>;<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">it <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumed</st> everything <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">around</st> it.<n id=\"7\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d3</span> (<i>Dalet</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01869\" class=\"\">prepared</st> his <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bow</st><n id=\"1\" /> like an <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">his <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right hand</st> <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">was ready</st> to shoot.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Like a <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">foe</st> he <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">everyone</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">even our <st data-num=\"04261 05869\">strong young men</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he has <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">poured out</st> his <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">anger</st> like <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st><p class=\"poetry\">on the <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tent</st><n id=\"4\" /> of <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d4</span> (<i>He</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> like an <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> her <st data-num=\"0759\" class=\"\">palaces</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">ruined</st> her<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortified cities</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">made everyone</st> in <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08386\" class=\"\">mourn</st> and <st data-num=\"0592\" class=\"\">lament</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d5</span> (<i>Vav</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"02554\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> his <st data-num=\"07900\" class=\"\">temple</st><n id=\"1\" /> as if it were a <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">vineyard</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> his <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">appointed meeting place</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has made those in <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forget</st><p class=\"poetry\">both the <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">festivals</st> and the <st data-num=\"07676\" class=\"\">Sabbaths</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">In his <st data-num=\"02195\" class=\"\">fierce</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st><n id=\"4\" /> he has <st data-num=\"05006\" class=\"\">spurned</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">both <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d6</span> (<i>Zayin</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02186\" class=\"\">rejected</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05010\" class=\"\">abhorred</st> his <st data-num=\"04720\" class=\"\">temple</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05462\" class=\"\">handed</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">over to</st> the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Jerusalem\u2019s <st data-num=\"0759\" class=\"\">palace</st> <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">walls</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the enemy<n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"06963 05414\">shouted</st><n id=\"6\" /> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st><p class=\"poetry\">as if it were a <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">feast</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d7</span> (<i>Khet</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> was <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">determined</st> to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">tear down</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">wall</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">prepared</st> <st data-num=\"06957\" class=\"\">to knock it down</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">withdraw</st> his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> from <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroying</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He made the <st data-num=\"02426\" class=\"\">ramparts</st> and fortified <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">walls</st> <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">lament</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st> they <st data-num=\"0535\" class=\"\">mourned</st> their ruin.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d8</span> (<i>Tet</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">city gates</st> have <st data-num=\"02883\" class=\"\">fallen</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">smashed</st> <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">to bits</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"01280\" class=\"\">bars</st> that lock her gates.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">princes</st> were taken into <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">exile</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is no</st> more <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">guidance</st> available.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">As for</st> her <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no longer</st> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">receive</st><n id=\"6\" /> a <st data-num=\"02377\" class=\"\">vision</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05d9</span> (<i>Yod</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sit</st><n id=\"1\" /> on the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> <st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">in silence</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">thrown</st> <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">dirt</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">heads</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they have <st data-num=\"02296\" class=\"\">dressed</st> in <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01330\" class=\"\">young women</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">stare</st> <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">down</st> at the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05db</span> (<i>Kaf</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">are worn out</st><n id=\"1\" /> from <st data-num=\"01832\" class=\"\">weeping</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">stomach</st> <st data-num=\"02560\" class=\"\">is in knots</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"03516\" class=\"\">heart</st><n id=\"4\" /> is <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">poured out</st> on the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">due to</st> the <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st><n id=\"5\" /> of my <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">helpless</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>;<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">children</st> and <st data-num=\"03243\" class=\"\">infants</st> <st data-num=\"05848\" class=\"\">faint</st><p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"07151\" class=\"\">town</st> <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">squares</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05dc</span> (<i>Lamed</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">Children<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st> to their <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mothers</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0346\" class=\"\">Where</st> are <st data-num=\"01715\" class=\"\">food</st> and <st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">drink</st>?\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05848\" class=\"\">faint</st><n id=\"4\" /> like a <st data-num=\"02491\" class=\"\">wounded</st> warrior<p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">squares</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">They</st> <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">die slowly</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">in</st> their <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mothers\u2019</st> <st data-num=\"02436\" class=\"\">arms</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05de</span> (<i>Mem</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">With <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> can I <st data-num=\"05749\" class=\"\">equate</st><n id=\"1\" /> you?<p class=\"poetry\">To <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> can I <st data-num=\"01819\" class=\"\">compare</st> you, O <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">To <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> can I <st data-num=\"07737\" class=\"\">liken</st> you<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so that<n id=\"3\" /> I might <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">comfort</st> you, O <st data-num=\"01330\" class=\"\">Virgin</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">wound</st> is as <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">deep</st><n id=\"4\" /> as the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> can <st data-num=\"07495\" class=\"\">heal</st> you?<n id=\"6\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e0</span> (<i>Nun</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> <st data-num=\"02372\" class=\"\">saw visions</st> for you<p class=\"poetry\">that were <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">worthless</st> <st data-num=\"08602\" class=\"\">whitewash</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">failed</st> to <st data-num=\"01540 05921\">expose</st> your <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sin</st><p class=\"poetry\">so as to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">restore</st> your <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">fortunes</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"02372\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"04864\" class=\"\">oracles</st> for you<p class=\"poetry\">that were <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">worthless</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"04065\" class=\"\">lies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e1</span> (<i>Samek</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> who <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passed by</st> on the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">road</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05606\" class=\"\">clapped</st> their <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hands</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to mock</st> you.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"08319\" class=\"\">sneered</st> and <st data-num=\"05128\" class=\"\">shook</st> their <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">heads</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cHa! Is <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">called</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018the <st data-num=\"03632\" class=\"\">perfection</st> of <st data-num=\"03308\" class=\"\">beauty</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"04885\" class=\"\">source of joy</st> of the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>!\u2019?\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e4</span> (<i>Pe</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> your <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06475 06310\">gloated</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> you.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"08319\" class=\"\">sneered</st> and <st data-num=\"02786\" class=\"\">gnashed</st> their <st data-num=\"08127\" class=\"\">teeth</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cWe have <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"2\" /> her!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">Ha</st>! We have <st data-num=\"06960\" class=\"\">waited</st> a long time for <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">We have <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">lived</st> to <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> it!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e2</span> (<i>Ayin</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> he <st data-num=\"02161\" class=\"\">planned</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he has <st data-num=\"01214\" class=\"\">fulfilled</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"0565\" class=\"\">promise</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> he <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">threatened</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">long</st> <st data-num=\"06924\" class=\"\">ago</st>:<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He has <st data-num=\"02040\" class=\"\">overthrown</st> you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">without</st> <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">mercy</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and has enabled the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> to <st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">gloat</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> you;<p class=\"poetry\">he has <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">exalted</st> your <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">adversaries\u2019</st> <st data-num=\"07161\" class=\"\">power</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><b><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e6</span></b> (<i>Tsade</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06817\" class=\"\">Cry out</st><n id=\"1\" /> from your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">O <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">wall</st> of <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Make your <st data-num=\"01832\" class=\"\">tears</st> <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">flow</st> like a <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">river</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03119\" class=\"\">all day</st> and <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">all night long</st>!<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05414 06314\">rest</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> let your <st data-num=\"01323 05869\">tears</st><n id=\"6\" /> <st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">stop</st>!</p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e7</span> (<i>Qof</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Get up</st>! <st data-num=\"07442\" class=\"\">Cry out</st> in the <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st> <p class=\"poetry\">when the <st data-num=\"0821\" class=\"\">night watches</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">start</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">Pour out</st> your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st><n id=\"2\" /> like <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05227\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">face</st> of the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">Lift up</st> your <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hands</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> your <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">children\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">lives</st>;<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they are <st data-num=\"05848\" class=\"\">fainting</st><n id=\"6\" />from <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">hunger</st> <p class=\"poetry\">at <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"02351\" class=\"\">street</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">corner</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e8</span> (<i>Resh</i>)<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Look</st>, O <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>! <st data-num=\"05027\" class=\"\">Consider</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Whom</st> have you ever <st data-num=\"05953\" class=\"\">afflicted</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">like this</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Should</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> their <st data-num=\"06529\" class=\"\">offspring</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"02949\" class=\"\">healthy</st> <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">infants</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Should</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> and <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> <p class=\"poetry\">be <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> in the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord\u2019s</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"04720\" class=\"\">sanctuary</st>?</p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05e9</span> (<i>Sin/Shin</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young boys</st> and <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">old men</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07901\" class=\"\">lie</st> dead on the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> in the <st data-num=\"02351\" class=\"\">streets</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"01330\" class=\"\">young women</st><n id=\"1\" /> and my <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st><p class=\"poetry\">have <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fallen</st> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> them <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">when</st> you were <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">angry</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"02873\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st> them <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">without</st> <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">mercy</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Lamentations",
    "chapter": "2",
    "text": "<p class=\"lamhebrew\"><span class=\"hebrew\">\u05ea</span> (<i>Tav</i>)<p class=\"poetry\">As if it were a <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">feast</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>, you <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">call</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">enemies<n id=\"2\" /> to <st data-num=\"04032\" class=\"\">terrify</st> me<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">on every side</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">On the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"01961 06412\">escaped</st> or <st data-num=\"08300\" class=\"\">survived</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> has <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">finished off</st><p class=\"poetry\">those healthy infants <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> I <st data-num=\"02946\" class=\"\">bore</st><n id=\"5\" /> and <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">raised</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  }
